data.description: Stunning 6BR, 4.5BA custom home w/finished basement, PLUS bonus rm upstairs (could be 7th BR). Prepare to be impressed the moment you enter this gorgeous home! Breathtaking two story foyer w/dual staircases. Gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream w/center isle breakfast bar, built-in appliances, soft-close cabinets w/glass doors & pull out storage racks, granite countertops & tile backsplash, PLUS butler's pantry w/wine bottle display cabinets. Family rm w/stacked stone wood burning fireplace. Breakfast rm & formal dining rm are perfect for holiday gatherings! Formal living rm could easily be used for home office or den/library. Owner's suite w/sitting rm & luxury private bath w/garden tub, separate walk-in tile shower & dual walk-in closets. Additional 3 BR's plus 2nd full bath upstairs, in addition to bonus rm. Main level guest suite w/full bath (3rd). Professionally finished basement offers massive rec rm, full kitchen with stainless appliances & breakfast bar, 6th BR, 4th full BA w/dual vanities & walk-in shower, PLUS fitness rm & mechanical rm w/2nd laundry connection. Nice lot w/fenced backyard and extended concrete patio. Side load 3 car garage w/extended driveway. WOW FACTOR 10++, YOU MUST SEE THIS HOME TO APPRECIATE. Too many features to list-see attachments for complete outline of upgrades. VETERANS CAN ASSUME VA LOAN @ 2.75%. SELLER WILL CONSIDER 5 YEAR CONTRACT SALE TO ALLEVIATE INTEREST RATE CONCERNS FOR BUYER.
